# Minimal structured `by induc` example.
# `prove induc:` proves the step under the default induction hypotheses.

abstract_prop p(a)

know:
    $p(0)
    forall n Z:
        n >= 0
        $p(n)
        =>:
            $p(n + 1)

by induc n from 0:
    prove:
        $p(n)

    prove from n = 0:
        $p(0)

    prove induc:
        $p(n + 1)

forall n Z:
    n >= 0
    =>:
        $p(n)
